Company Overview of Brevan Howard Capital Management, LP



Snapshot People




Company Overview
Brevan Howard Capital Management, LP is a privately owned hedge fund sponsor. The firm invests in alternative investment markets across the globe. Brevan Howard Capital Management, LP is based in Jersey, Channel Islands.


